'''林駑'''，[[表字|字]]景文，[[号|号]]东湖{{efn|name=ab2}}，[[明朝|明朝]]前期，[[泉州_(景云)|泉州]]商人{{efn|name=ab1}}{{efn|name=ab2}}。[[李贄|李贄]]的祖先。

其家族本为李姓。根据《荣山李氏族谱》、《凤池林李宗谱》等资料，可知一世祖李辅官是唐朝[[光啟|光啟]]二年（886年）定居[[泉州_(景云)|泉州]]。其父李闾为第十九世祖，改姓為[[林閭|林閭]]，成为林（李）氏始祖<ref name=aa1/>{{Rp|5}}。明[[洪武|洪武]]九年（1376年）{{efn|name=ab1|赵青文章中《荣山李氏族谱》的记载<ref name=aa1/>{{Rp|5}}：“驽字景文，东湖长子，航吴泛越，为泉巨商。洪武丙辰九年，奉命发舶西洋，娶色目人，逐习其俗，终身不革。今子孙蕃衍，犹不去其异教[……]恐后世子孙，仍袭其弊者，以特严戒之云尔[……]”。}}，或称洪武十七年（1384年）{{efn|name=ab2|赵青文章中《凤池林李宗谱》的记载<ref name=aa1/>{{Rp|5}}：“公讳驽，字景文，号东湖，始祖睦斋公长子也。为泉巨商。洪武十七年，奉命发航西洋，忽鲁谟斯等教不一，为事不谐，行年三十，遂从其教，受戒于举清净寺教门，号顺天之民。就娶色目婢人归于家，卒年四十六。吾宗七世以上，犹葬用槨，其祖谐此乎？然而肇分林李之派，其隙亦开于此矣。”}}，林駑前往[[忽鲁谟斯|忽鲁谟斯]]，皈依[[伊斯蘭教|伊斯蘭教]]，隨後娶了“[[色目人|色目]]婢人”（[[波斯人|波斯人]]或[[阿拉伯人|阿拉伯人]]），并攜此女返回泉州定居。卒年四十六{{efn|name=ab2}}。<ref>{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=067On0JgItAC&pg=PA817&dq=ch'ang+fond+persian+girl&hl=en&ei=5wEsTJesKMT_lgfR5KHnCQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=10&ved=0CFwQ6AEwCQ#v=onepage&q=li%20nu%20married%20an%20arab%20or%20persian%20girl&f=false|title=A-L, Volumes 1-2|author=Association for Asian studies (Ann Arbor;Michigan)|year=1976|publisher=Columbia University Press|location=|page=817|isbn=0-231-03801-1|accessdate=2010-06-29|archive-date=2020-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200609053742/https://books.google.com/books?id=067On0JgItAC&pg=PA817&dq=ch%27ang+fond+persian+girl&hl=en&ei=5wEsTJesKMT_lgfR5KHnCQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=10&ved=0CFwQ6AEwCQ#v=onepage&q=li%20nu%20married%20an%20arab%20or%20persian%20girl&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Chen">{{cite web|url=http://www.iranicaonline.org/articles/chinese-iranian-vii|title=CHINESE-IRANIAN RELATIONS vii. Persian Settlements in Southeastern China during the T'ang, Sung, and Yuan Dynasties|last=Chen|first=Da-Sheng|publisher=Encyclopedia Iranica|accessdate=2010-06-28|archive-date=2011-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110429174424/http://www.iranicaonline.org/articles/chinese-iranian-vii|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=l6TVhvYLaEwC&pg=PA495&dq=li+nu+persian+girl&hl=en&ei=kw8sTKShEsP7lwespayLCg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CDMQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=li%20nu%20persian%20girl&f=false|title=Science and civilisation in China, Volume 4|author=Joseph Needham|year=1971|publisher=Cambridge University Press|location=|page=495|isbn=0-521-07060-0|accessdate=2010-06-29|archive-date=2020-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200612185727/https://books.google.com/books?id=l6TVhvYLaEwC&pg=PA495&dq=li+nu+persian+girl&hl=en&ei=kw8sTKShEsP7lwespayLCg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CDMQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=li%20nu%20persian%20girl&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=067On0JgItAC&pg=PA817&dq=He+writes:+%22Li+Nu+Hg+who+was+at+Ormuz+in+1337,+married+an+Arab+or+Persian+girl+and+adopted+Islam&hl=en&ei=mk1TTbu8PIP7lweU0N2hCg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCcQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=He%20writes%3A%20%22Li%20Nu%20Hg%20who%20was%20at%20Ormuz%20in%201337%2C%20married%20an%20Arab%20or%20Persian%20girl%20and%20adopted%20Islam&f=false|title=Dictionary of Ming biography, 1368-1644|author=Association for Asian Studies. Ming Biographical History Project Committee, Luther Carrington Goodrich, Chao-ying Fang|year=1976|publisher=Columbia University Press|location=|page=817|isbn=0-231-03801-1|accessdate=February 9, 2011|archive-date=2020-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200612185739/https://books.google.com/books?id=067On0JgItAC&pg=PA817&dq=He+writes:+%22Li+Nu+Hg+who+was+at+Ormuz+in+1337,+married+an+Arab+or+Persian+girl+and+adopted+Islam&hl=en&ei=mk1TTbu8PIP7lweU0N2hCg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCcQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=He%20writes%3A%20%22Li%20Nu%20Hg%20who%20was%20at%20Ormuz%20in%201337%2C%20married%20an%20Arab%20or%20Persian%20girl%20and%20adopted%20Islam&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1980年代以后，中外研究者对李贽的研究中，通常将林駑“娶色目女”改信伊斯兰教，视为伊斯兰教影响李贽思想的依据<ref name="aa1">{{cite thesis|url=https://www.zhangqiaokeyan.com/academic-degree-domestic_mphd_thesis/020314305419.html|chapter=|title=迷雾中的真实——辨析李贽与伊斯兰教有无确切关系|format=|author=赵青|degree=硕士|accessdate=2021-04-30|year=2015|publisher=上海师范大学|quote=|language=Zh-hans|archive-date=2021-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210501093030/https://www.zhangqiaokeyan.com/academic-degree-domestic_mphd_thesis/020314305419.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{Rp|3}}。研究者赵青认为“林驽和李贽相隔六代，在没有文献资料证实中间几代先祖有信仰伊斯兰的情况下，因为林驽是穆斯林所以认为李贽也是穆斯林显然是说不通的”。同时，赵青指出，林驽之子、李贽三世祖李允诚随堂兄弟李广斋迁居[[南安县|南安县]]，同样改回李姓。李广斋激烈反对伯父林驽的伊斯兰教信仰<ref name=aa1/>{{Rp|11、12}}。

